ca.mcgill.hs.plugin
Class TDEClassifierPlugin

java.lang.Object
  ca.mcgill.hs.plugin.OutputPlugin
      ca.mcgill.hs.plugin.TDEClassifierPlugin
All Implemented Interfaces:
Plugin, java.lang.Runnable
public final class TDEClassifierPlugin
extends OutputPlugin

Currently classifies motion status into moving or lingering based on a simple threshold over a moving average of the accelerometer magnitudes. Also classifies according to time-delay embedding models (Frank et al, 2010) if they exist in the models folder.
